{
  "id": "adv_event_2407_01_01",
  "title": "誰が雑魚\nアイドルよ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "千紗、今日のダンスレッスンいい感じだったじゃない\n伸び伸びと踊れていてとても良かったわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚ today's dance lesson went really well‚ didn't it?\nYou were dancing so freely and it was really good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.6860090256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、怜ちゃん\nでも、私なんてまだまだだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ Rei-chan.\nBut I'm still nowhere near good enough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.9,
      "endTime": 15.019365024499999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないわ。最近は弱気になることも減って\n自分の意志も言えるようになってきていたじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true. Lately you've been less timid\nand you've started being able to express your own will.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2333333333,
      "endTime": 22.873991044300002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗はちゃんと成長してるんだから、自信を持って\n言いたいことを言って、やりたいことをやりなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚ you're properly growing‚ so have confidence.\nSay what you want to say‚ and do what you want to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.0666666667,
      "endTime": 30.5947617213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "言いたいこと……じゃ、じゃあ、怜ちゃん……！\nあの、えっと……ごめん、なんでもない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What I want to say… th-then‚ Rei-chan…!\nUm‚ well… sorry‚ it's nothing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.8,
      "endTime": 40.4095006943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "千紗……言いたいことがあるなら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa… if you have something to say…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.5999992371,
      "endTime": 43.5826521874,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3166.6643778999983
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "大変だよ！　大ニュースだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is terrible! Big news!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.166663615,
      "endTime": 48.9537155788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "さくら！？　そんなに慌ててどうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura!? Why are you in such a panic?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.166663615,
      "endTime": 52.506822363599994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "サニピにテレビの出演依頼が来たんだよ！\nそれがゴールデンタイムの特番なんだけどね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace got a TV appearance request!\nIt's a golden time special‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.6999969483,
      "endTime": 60.333331871,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "人気番組なのに出演拒否する人が続出したせいで\n最近は放送されていない地獄のロケ企画なんだって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is the hellish location project that hasn't recently been broadcast‚\nbecause so many people refused to appear despite its popularity!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.4999966939,
      "endTime": 70.7807906469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！\n地獄のロケ企画ってどういうことですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nWhat do you mean by hellish location project!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.0666633606,
      "endTime": 78.16285362250001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、落ち着いて\nちゃんと説明するから話を聞いてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ calm down.\nI'll explain properly‚ so please listen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.3666633606,
      "endTime": 82.911130333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "今回オファーが来たのは、『アイドル極限サバイバル\n無人島脱出スペシャル』という番組だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The offer we received this time is for \"Idol Extreme\nSurvival Deserted Island Escape Special\".",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1000012715,
      "endTime": 89.10730288810001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは……今まで無数のアイドルが脱出に失敗して\n海の藻屑となって消えていった伝説の企画……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-that's… the legendary project where countless idols\nfailed to escape and vanished into the sea…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.3000012715,
      "endTime": 98.3557385762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "海の藻屑にはなってないぞ\nみんなリタイアしただけで消えてはいないからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They didn’t vanish into the sea.\nEveryone just retired and didn't disappear.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.5666679382,
      "endTime": 103.5723397255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "その番組って、アイドルが無人島に置き去りにされて\nサバイバルしながら島からの脱出を目指すのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That show is where idols are abandoned on a deserted island\nand aim to escape while surviving‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.76667099,
      "endTime": 112.1414104462,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "あまりにも過酷過ぎて心が折れるアイドルが続出……\n今まで100組が挑戦して脱出成功は一組だけ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So many idols broke down because it was too harsh…\nOut of 100 groups that tried‚ only one succeeded in escaping…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.3333376567,
      "endTime": 121.6892334621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "成功率1パーセント……\n確かにそれは過酷な企画だわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1 percent success rate…\nThat certainly is a harsh project.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.9000043233,
      "endTime": 128.3627478917,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "最近は特に多忙で疲れているみんなに、こんなロケは\nさせられない。だから、このオファーは断るつもりだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone's been especially busy and tired lately‚ so I can't\nmake you do this kind of location shoot. So I plan to decline this offer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.56667099,
      "endTime": 136.195809269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、無人島でサバイバルってことは……\n夏の海でキャンプするってことですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But surviving on a deserted island means…\ncamping by the summer ocean‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.4000043233,
      "endTime": 145.2461716969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "だったら私、やってみたいです！\nみんなと無人島でキャンプなんて絶対楽しいよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that's the case‚ I want to try it!\nCamping on a deserted island with everyone would definitely be fun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.4333376567,
      "endTime": 153.0464670817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "出たわね、さくらのポジティブシンキング……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There it is‚ Sakura's positive thinking…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.2333376567,
      "endTime": 157.1301856677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "実は私もちょっと興味あるのよね\nみんなとキャンプしたいなーって思ってたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ I'm a little interested too\nBecause I was thinking I'd like to camp with everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.3333376567,
      "endTime": 165.1050154369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "場所は南の島……真夏の海……\n水着のアイドルとずっと一緒……良き……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The location is a southern island… midsummer ocean…\nalways together with idols in swimsuits… good…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.3000043233,
      "endTime": 171.8930879911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "ソロキャンパーとドルオタが何か言ってるわね\n現実的に考えて、今の私達のスケジュールじゃ厳しいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The solo camper and idol otaku are saying something.\nThinking realistically‚ it's tough with our current schedule.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.1000043233,
      "endTime": 180.5293464025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに、無人島から脱出成功した唯一のアイドルは\n元BIG4のどりきゅん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ the only idol who successfully escaped from the deserted island\nwas DoriKyun from the former BIG4…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.7333376567,
      "endTime": 187.57828098939999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "どりきゅんはインタビューで「雑魚アイドルには\n無理だからやめた方がいい」って言ってる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "DoriKyun said in an interview‚\n\"It's impossible for weaklings—just give up.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.76667099,
      "endTime": 193.93356666559998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_01_01-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "誰が雑魚アイドルよ！　いいわ、最速で脱出して\n私達の方がどりきゅんより上だって証明してあげる！",
      "translations": {
